snippet.title: Luna Online Gameplay First Look HD - MMOs.com
snippet.description:
http://mmos.com/review/luna-online for Luna Online reviews, videos, screenshots, music and more!

Browse through hundreds of free to play MMOs and MMORPGs at http://mmos.com

Luna Online first look gameplay video + commentary by Omer from MMOs.com

Luna Online is a free to play anime inspired MMORPG with cute graphics. It originally launched in the West in ~2009 , but shut down when gPotato closed it. Now it's available through SubaGames - the Necromancer of MMOs.
